<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Court-Mais-Trash (CMT) - ESSEC</title>
    <link href="/lib/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/lib/css/stylesheet.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/lib/open-iconic/font/css/open-iconic-bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet">    
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --essec-blue: #1d9edd;
            --essec-dark-blue: #005587;
            --essec-light-blue: #e6f3fa;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--essec-light-blue);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: var(--essec-blue);
            color: white;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h3 {
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        h4 {
            color: var(--essec-dark-blue);
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .input-group {
            display: flex;
            border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .input-group:focus-within {
            border-color: var(--essec-blue);
        }
        .input-group-prepend {
            background-color: var(--essec-light-blue);
            padding: 0.75rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            color: var(--essec-blue);
        }
        .form-control {
            flex-grow: 1;
            border: none;
            padding: 0.75rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .form-control:focus {
            outline: none;
        }
        .btn {
            background-color: var(--essec-blue);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: var(--essec-dark-blue);
        }
        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
        }
        .text-muted {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .input-addon{
            background-color: #E9ECEF;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border: 2px solid var(--input-border);
            border-left: none;
            border-top-right-radius: 2px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 2px;
            color: #6C757D;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .text-danger {
            color: #dc3545;
        }
        .text-success {
            color: #28a745;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--essec-dark-blue);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h3>Bienvenue sur le site du Court-Mais-Trash</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h4 class="text-center">Retrouvez votre compte</h4>
            <p class="text-center text-muted">Veuillez saisir votre BannerID afin que nous puissions vous envoyer un mail de récupération de mot de passe.</p>
            <% if(info != "") { %>
                <p class="text-center text-success"><%= info.message %></p>
            <% } %>
            <% if(error != "") { %>
                <p class="text-center text-danger"><%= error.message %></p>
            <% } %>
            <form method="post" action="/forgotten-password">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <!-- <div class="input-group-prepend">
                            <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                        </div> -->
    
                        <input name="bannerid" class="form-control" placeholder="BannerID (B00...)" type="text"/>
                        <small class="text-muted input-addon ">@essec.edu</small>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn">Envoyer</button>
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">Annuler</a>
            </form>
            <p class="text-center text-muted">En cas de problème, vous pouvez nous contacter à contact@bde-essec.fr</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Fait avec ❤️ par BDE x Digital Hippo </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>